messageBody:
I am in the process of profiling Java programs using the Java Virtual
Machine Profiler Interface. In the past I have only been running
Benchmark Suites but I wish to move on to real world GUI programs.
I would like to know if Abbot is suitable for such a task and if not
would there be any other alternatives.

Any help would be greatly appreciated.
